houserelays (1.8) UNRELEASED; urgency=low

   * Conform to the latest house control API documentation.
   * Performance improvements.
   * Manage the depot API in houseconfig.c for more consistent rules between depot and local file storage.
   * Fix time size mismatch (Linux 64 bit time on 32 bit architecture).
   * Support poll for changes mechanism.
   * Fix GPIOD2 regression and use gpiod bias when active low.
   * Add basic trigger feature to the web UI.
   * Allow adjusting the sampling rate from the WEB UI and from the client.
   * New change history design: return list of timed changes.
   * Keep change history and normal scan consistent.
   * Switch to libgpiod3.

 -- Pascal Martin <pascal.fb.martin@gmail.com>  Thu, 9 Apr 2026 12:00:00 PDT

